#BUSCO v1,1 release notes

http://busco.ezlab.org
Wed May 20 10:49:32 2015
-------------------------------------------------

Version 1.1b includes the following changes:

- Lineage sets may now be specified using the full path (e.g. -l /path/to/lineage)

Version 1.1 includes the following changes:

- Threading support for gene prediction, yielding significant speed gains on genome mode.
- Added checks to make sure the necessary software is set-up correctly